2011-07-08T03:48:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/ebm-technologies-june-sales-fall-56-46-table-8409-tt.html
EBM TECHNOLOGIES said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 56.46% to NT$21,955,000 from NT$50,427,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             21,955           50,427    
YOY%             -56.46%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             70,127          100,645    
YOY%             -30.32% 
=================================================================
 